### Jamf Protect

This Kibana dashboard features a range of visualizations highlighting key events and the most recent alerts. It serves as a customizable template, allowing adjustments to meet specific organizational needs.

query.query: event.module: "jamf_protect"  and event.kind:"alert" and event.severity: ("0" or "4")
event.module:"jamf_protect" and event.kind:"alert" and event.severity: ("2" or "6")
event.module : "jamf_protect" and event.kind:"alert" and (event.severity: 3  or event.severity: 8)

panelsJSON.title: Top processes related to detection and hostname
Top 10 process shahex values by process executable

query.query: observer.product : "Jamf Protect" and event.kind:"alert" and NOT process.code_signature.signing_id:com.apple.*

embeddableConfig.description: Apple's signed binaries are not bound to an TeamID.

panelsJSON.title: Top process Signing Information by TeamID
